able to eventually punish those trying to damage the country's
reputation, interests and status.
</P>
<P>
Iranian-backed Hezbollah, or Party of God, which is
spearheading a military campaign to oust Israeli troops from south
Lebanon, also issued a statement condemning Egyptian
fundamentalist militants who killed at least 77 people.
</P>
