all Afghan parties and those countries and organizations who were
interested in Afghanistan urgently needed to cooperate with UN to
put an end to the senseless conflict which had caused so much
suffering and damage to the Afghan people.
</P>
<P>
Reports say that as many as 2,000 fighters from the Islamic
Taliban Movement were killed and buries in mass graves after taken
prisoners in northern Afghanistan by forces of the coalition
driven out of Kabul last year. 
