Albina Assis, Angolan Minister of Petroleum, said the
country's petroleum industry is now in a new stage which requires
advanced technologies to deal with oil tapping in a complicated
environment.
</P>
<P>
She believed that the British Petroleum Corporation will help
the development of the industry in Angola.
</P>
<P>
