<HEADLINE> International Stamps and Coins Exhibition Opens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, November 19 (Xinhua) -- An international exhibition
on stamps and coins opened at the Shanghai Exhibition Center here
today.
</P>
<P>
Postal agents, stamp and coin traders as well as state mints
and stamp companies from over 100 countries and regions have
brought their new or unique exhibits to the current show.
</P>
<P>
Each of the five days during the exhibition will be featured by
a dominant theme such as the China Stamps Day and Youth Stamps and
Coins Day, said the organizer.
</P>
<P>
Sales booths have been set up to satisfy the needs of stamps
and coins lovers. 
</P>
