<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, Vietnam, November 19 (Xinhua) -- Men's top seed Hernawan
Susanto was knocked out of running in the first round match of the
Vietnam badminton open Wednesday by unseeded Thomas Johansson of
Sweden.
