(the lower house of Indian parliament) Speaker P.A. Sangma and
some other Indian leaders and parliamentarians.
</P>
<P>
After her talks with Gujral, the two sides signed an investment
incentive agreement to promote and protect private U.S. investment
in India and an agreement for establishing an Indo-U.S. science
and technology forum for promoting research cooperation between
scientists of the two countries.
</P>
<P>
Albright is the first U.S. secretary of state to visit India in
14 years. 
