the outlook is poor," said one local broker.
</P>
<P>
Total market volume increased to 212.61 million units, valued
at 415.34 million Singapore dollars (259.59 million US dollars).
Declines overwhelmed advances by 291 to 68, while 252 other
counters remained unchanged.
</P>
<P>
