end at 13.5 Singapore dollars. Roth M. 200 increased by 60 cents
to close at 14 Singapore dollars, while NBT gained 30 cents to
finish at 22.3 Singapore dollars.
</P>
<P>
On the downside, DBS Foreign was the biggest loser as it
declined by 1.4 dollars to close at 13.2 Singapore dollars.
Innovest Bhd fell by 73 cents to finish at 1.1 dollars. The
Singapore Press Holdings (SPH) Foreign lost 70 cents to end at
20.6 Singapore dollars.  
